---
import BuiltByDrizzleTeam from "@/ui/components/BuiltByDrizzleTeam.astro";
import Layout from "../ui/Layout.astro";
import Showcase from "@/content/landing/showcase.mdx";
---

<Layout title="Waddler">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="landing__wrap">
      <div class="landing__title-wrap">
        <span class="landing__duck-emoji">ðŸ¦†</span>
        <div class="landing__title">Waddler</div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing__description">
        Unify your database communication in JS and TS
      </div>
      <div class="landing__name-meaning">
       Built <a href="https://drizzle.team">by drizzle.team</a>
      </div>
      <BuiltByDrizzleTeam />
      <a href="/docs/overview" class="landing__documentation-btn"
        ><div>Documentation</div>
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
        >
          <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
          <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="landing__body">
    Waddler is a database client wrapper that unifies database communication and enables
    <b>all</b>* supported database clients to use an SQL template 
    tag with consistent syntax, value escaping, helping prevent SQL 
    injection and supporting common query-building scenarios.
    <p style="font-size: 14px; font-style: italic;">
    <br>* supported clients by waddler
    </p>
    <div class="landing__subbody">
    You don't need to learn each driver's API, hunt for the features you need to build 
    queries, or constantly write your own small utilities for parameterization, escaping, 
    and so on. All of that is handled by the <b>sql``</b> template tag from Waddler
    </div>
    </div>
    <Showcase />
  </div>
  <script></script>
  <style>
    html[class~="dark"] .landing__title {
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }
    html[class~="dark"] .landing__description {
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    html[class~="dark"] .landing__body {
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    html[class~="dark"] .landing__subbody {
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    html[class~="dark"] .landing__name-meaning {
      color: #999;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: 100%;
      height: fit-content;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 72px;
      padding: 100px 0;
    }
    .landing__wrap {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .landing__title-wrap {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .landing__title {
      margin-left: 4px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .landing__duck-emoji {
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 36px;
    }

    .landing__description {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .landing__body {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 0px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .landing__subbody {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .landing__name-meaning {
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #727272;
    }

    html[class~="dark"] .landing__documentation-btn {
      background-color: #e2e8f0;
      color: #282828;
    }

    .landing__documentation-btn {
      margin-top: 80px;
      width: 212px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      height: 48px;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: none;
      background-color: #282b3b;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .landing__documentation-btn svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
    }
  </style>
  <script>
    window.addEventListener("beforeunload", () => {
      localStorage.setItem("sidebar-scroll", "0");
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
